{"tid":1433300,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【保護利君雅BB】利君雅被DQ，手足一齊send 信比 聯合國消除種族歧視委員會","createTime":"2019-08-08T12:38:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T12:47:43.000Z","uid":54337,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ca36294ee94eefddc744c0b8572cb145209dd77a","tid":1433300,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:38:24.000Z","msg":"港台公然歧視南亞裔女士<br />\n手足一齊send 信比聯合國消除種族歧視委員會 (OHCHR)<br />\n<br />\nFrom wiki :<br />\n《消除一切形式種族歧視國際公約》（英語：Convention on the Elimination of All Forms of Racial Discrimination, ICERD）是一項聯合國公約。作為第三代人權文件，公約要求其締約國消除種族歧視和促進所有種族間的諒解。該公約也要求各國以法律禁止仇恨言論，並以刑事手段懲治種族主義組織。<br />\n<br />\n官方網站：<a href=\"https://www.ohchr.org/EN/pages/home.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ohchr.org%2FEN%2Fpages%2Fhome.aspx&d=lkc5f2JhJq%2FgDjyEy7Hc9UbB09kggXsiIZ7Oz%2FeLJLU%3D&h=f0e50713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ohchr.org/EN/pages/home.aspx</a><br />\nEmail : InfoDesk@ohchr.org"},{"pid":"98b7583c3f2ecda922c7ed8473a7b756e49daf1e","tid":1433300,"uid":7818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:40:00.000Z","msg":"依家關種族歧視咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a35aa5bf1395f538e12f2f1d229e149d84ef7dde","tid":1433300,"uid":20916,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:40:55.000Z","msg":"唔係未confirm咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17be672bcca61a314def490152a77caa336611cc","tid":1433300,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T12:41:41.000Z","msg":"推到克警仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/k